#: assets/js/blocks/paymos-blocks.js:9
msgid "Pay with USDT or USDC across 13 networks — Tron, Ethereum, Polygon, Base, Solana and more. No price volatility, no chargebacks, settlement on-chain in minutes."
msgstr "Оплата в USDT или USDC в 13 сетях — Tron, Ethereum, Polygon, Base, Solana и других. Без скачков курса, без чарджбэков, расчёт on-chain за минуты."

